6-02 |accessdate=2017-11-06 |archive-date=2017-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008231101/https://www.postcrossing.com/blog/2015/06/02/30-million-postcards |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第四千万张是一张来自[[臺灣|臺灣]]寄往[[法國|法國]]的明信片<ref name="40 million postcards">{{en}} {{cite web |author=meiadeleite |url=https://www.postcrossing.com/blog/2017/02/13/40-million-postcards |title=40 Million Postcards! |work=Postcrossing.com |date=2015-02-13 |accessdate=2017-11-06 |archive-date=2017-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008231140/https://www.postcrossing.com/blog/2017/02/13/40-million-postcards |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第五千万张是一张来自以色列寄往[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]的明信片。<ref name="50! MILLION! POSTCARDS!">{{en}} {{cite web |author=meiadeleite |url=https://www.postcrossing.com/blog/2018/12/27/50-million-postcards |title=50! MILLION! POSTCARDS! |work=Postcrossing.com |date=2018-12-27 |accessdate=2019-01-04 |archive-date=2019-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104175955/https://www.postcrossing.com/blog/2018/12/27/50-million-postcards |dead-url=no }}</ref>

